Note version_history: '''
# Schema Version History

## v1.1 (2026-03-26) - CRITICAL FIXES
**Status:** PRODUCTION READY

### Fixed Critical Issues:
1. **BR-004 Enforcement** - Added trigger to prevent booking delegated HBLs / delegating booked HBLs
2. **BR-001 Validation** - Application layer (see booking-readiness.ts)
3. **Derived Fields** - Removed chargeable_weight, storage_fee_applicable; do_waived now generated column
4. **GST Constraints** - Added check constraints on all GST calculations (±1¢ tolerance)
5. **BR-015 Audit** - Added cutoff_override_by_user_id, reason, timestamp to bookings
6. **BR-028 Automation** - Background job (see update-booking-collected-status.ts)

### Other Improvements:
- Added entity_audit_log table for comprehensive audit trail
- Added optimistic locking (version columns) to bookings, slots, hbls
- Added email retry mechanism (retry_count, next_retry_at, max_retries)
- Converted payment_gateway to enum (stripe | compay)
- Converted related_entity_type to enum for type safety
- Added soft-delete (archived_at) to companies, driver_records for consistency
- Added uploaded_by_user_id to delivery_orders
- Added last_edited_by_user_id to hbls (acfs:r12)

### Migration Notes:
- Safe to run on empty database (no data migration needed)
- All changes are additive except:
  - DROP COLUMN hbls.chargeable_weight
  - DROP COLUMN hbls.storage_fee_applicable
  - ALTER COLUMN hbls.do_waived (make generated)
  - ALTER COLUMN payments.payment_gateway (varchar → enum)
  - ALTER COLUMN email_notifications.related_entity_type (varchar → enum)

---

## v1.0 (2026-03-25) - Initial Production Schema
- Merged Intent Model v0.8.0 + VBS_DBML operational enhancements
- Implements all BR-001 through BR-033
- Australian GST and CoR compliance

---

Generated: 2026-03-26
Last Updated: 2026-03-26
Status: PRODUCTION READY ✅
